{"tid":1233980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再唔散係咪想變雨傘2.0失敗收場？","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T00:14:56.000Z","uid":124859,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4f07ce2efd9ac7d582536b1de546b425d4b9e2","tid":1233980,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"唔好死佔爛佔消耗體力又無意思<br />\n雨傘2.0就係咁樣失敗收場<br />\n依家需要打游擊，我都唔係要你搞革命，好似巴士底監獄，但至少可仿效法國黃背心運動<br />\n<br />\n依家佔住夏愨道真係無意思，我地計劃下一次行動好過，截至目前777仲未做到我地任何一個訴求，烈士一個遺願都未做到。<br />\n<br />\n1. 䆁放被捕人士<br />\n2. 追究警方責任<br />\n3. 完成撒回條例"},{"pid":"efb1302819984d8deba91969039a399ad8106551","tid":1233980,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c536a9c247011589279cb8c6cef3d7c04f33ee75","tid":1233980,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14cfac90434f91ff6cb546dac49dbf8b0f7ddc82","tid":1233980,"uid":29608,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:03:07.000Z","msg":"散啦，依家基本上已經贏哂社會認同<br />\n<br />\n再唔走又輸返"},{"pid":"3c8c20c25ee9fb314bf3d7d7d7a803d894b688db","tid":1233980,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:03:36.000Z","msg":"好想現場既人明白"},{"pid":"0c01f8e59aa32aa11a628f9dc20d8dc0fc6a28dd","tid":1233980,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:06:07.000Z","msg":"夠人時唔衝<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人時死守<br />\n<br />\n唉, 我都唔知點搞?<br />\n<br />\n總之快D撤, 好危險"},{"pid":"a60d9a83c4faa9ac4bf2dc55b1d0628724ea9e0d","tid":1233980,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:07:21.000Z","msg":"大推！"},{"pid":"d5be00df64a267127fdcebd8f0f7df0014c0e439","tid":1233980,"uid":241101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:08:04.000Z","msg":"Exacty要識玩政治<br />\n責任喺我地度就有位卑人入<br />\n而最重要，政府玩野我地一樣可以馬上動員阻止，到時出黎做野就都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />no loss仲要出師有名拎埋光環<br />\n<br />\n大丈夫能申、亦能「屈」<br />\n屈唔係委屈，而係穩定軍心預備定一個更好嘅時勢而行動<br />\n唔好送人頭卑人<br />\n依家時勢沉住道氣都可以卑到政府壓力<br />\n<br />\nPS 我一直尊重前線嘅勇士，抗爭路上冇左你地都唔得<br />\n依家係整合隊形時間、等對方出牌<br />\n同抵制分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ce3507b068a78f0246feaec7056abc583a1271","tid":1233980,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:08:40.000Z","msg":"你200萬01人上街<br />\n政府都無理呢過3個訴求<br />\n下一次行動? 你覺得點做佢先會回應你?"},{"pid":"42312bf388a75daac63b9e094526951b6792bfda","tid":1233980,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:09:28.000Z","msg":"販民情意結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4073260b005038efa7248b942aeb14849e7d3b","tid":1233980,"uid":188671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:09:56.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ce2fce88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"},{"pid":"d7639161bea39c00504ba1fca45ca713ab3d82e5","tid":1233980,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f2ca81631a4a4f9d84559e30deac0919dd06fdc","tid":1233980,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ce3507b068a78f0246feaec7056abc583a1271","tid":1233980,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco